{"tid":871313,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲既生活同我一樣😭","createTime":"2018-10-21T23:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T08:11:09.000Z","uid":35300,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"15814fd643ecffed42eb00440aaeeb41ce4e698c","tid":871313,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:49:07.000Z","msg":"日日返工都等緊放假，但係到咗放假嗰日，發現好似仲悶過返工。<br />\n返工嗰陣都叫做可以搵啲同事傾吓計，但係到放假就自己一個望住4面牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己朋友又唔多，平時都無人會約我出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最慘嘅係，人大咗對打機又無以前咁沉迷，想養隻貓陪吓自己，屋企人又唔鐘意。<br />\n所以有時真係覺得放假好苦悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdc65dea979b4c8618f814dc1544466da3083a7","tid":871313,"uid":163937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:55:21.000Z","msg":"啱呀 除咗星期五晚去happy hour 其他時間基本上都生不如死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10825b6143c5c9d7f368e9cb93dad9f254393a20","tid":871313,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:57:11.000Z","msg":"PMED"},{"pid":"5529b72ea52f478db0854dc0aea817c7d20c42c1","tid":871313,"uid":42402,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:59:02.000Z","msg":"一樣 會諗返工到底為乜 <br />\n<br />\n努力搵錢最後朋友唔多個 女又冇<br />\n<br />\n最後諗埋之後仲有幾十年 就想死"},{"pid":"ef4a2e179a1e235a866219ae7c3a848cfa2995bb","tid":871313,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放假嘅唯一娛樂就係搵戲睇，或者去書店打書釘<br />\n但無都係得自由一個，係人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bb49d58dc07c31d81c8edecc8c411745344a29","tid":871313,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4a2e179a1e235a866219ae7c3a848cfa2995bb","tid":871313,"uid":35300,"l